title: NFL Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 7
itunes:title: NFL Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 7
description:
It's the Bloomberg Business of Sports Fantasy Football Podcast! Hosts Michael Barr, Damian Sassower and Richard Trueman recap Week 6 which featured more subpar performances from a few big name QBs. They discuss their picks and predictions for Week 7.
